Package org.timepedia.chronoscope.client.gss.parser

Class Summary
GssParser Parser for GSS text format, loosely based on CSS.
GssProperty Represents a GSS property declaration
GssRule Represents a GSS rule defined by a list of selectors and corresponding list of properties to be applied.
GssSelector Represents a single selector formed by simple selectors separated by combinators.
GssStylesheetGssContext A Gss context which relies on parsed GSS text stylesheets
 

Exception Summary
GssParseException
